01:04:20,390 --> 01:04:22,130
<b>I don't have that, so let's just eat.</b>

706
01:04:23,460 --> 01:04:24,500
<b>Okay.</b>

707
01:04:29,240 --> 01:04:30,370
<b>Frying pan.</b>

708
01:04:30,940 --> 01:04:32,970
<b>"That" was a frying pan.</b>

709
01:04:46,650 --> 01:04:48,590
<b>There was a time when I didn't sleep for a month.</b>

710
01:04:49,660 --> 01:04:50,660
<b>Why not?</b>

711
01:04:53,560 --> 01:04:55,060
<b>Right before I left Oslo.</b>

712
01:05:18,850 --> 01:05:21,150
<b>It may seem strange to others.</b>

713
01:05:23,490 --> 01:05:26,290
<b>Not sleeping, not eating at mealtimes,</b>

714
01:05:27,330 --> 01:05:29,300
<b>not caring if the living room and bedroom are indistinguishable,</b>

715
01:05:30,300 --> 01:05:31,460
<b>not settling down in a place.</b>

716
01:05:33,030 --> 01:05:35,270
<b>That's how I am, and I'm used to it.</b>

717
01:05:41,910 --> 01:05:43,580
<b>It's the same blanket.</b>

718
01:05:45,040 --> 01:05:46,780
<b>You said you slept well because of the blanket,</b>

719
01:05:47,750 --> 01:05:49,280
<b>because it crinkled since it was new.</b>

720
01:05:52,820 --> 01:05:55,220
<b>In the spring and fall, if it gets sunny out,</b>

721
01:05:55,220 --> 01:05:58,220
<b>Eun Joo and I hang the blankets out in the sun.</b>

722
01:05:58,860 --> 01:06:00,730
<b>I sleep the best on those nights.</b>

723
01:06:06,600 --> 01:06:08,870
<b>I should hang a clothesline in the front yard.</b>

724
01:06:11,540 --> 01:06:12,640
<b>Let's do that.</b>

725
01:06:20,080 --> 01:06:22,420
<b>I'll leave once you fall asleep.</b>

726
01:06:22,750 --> 01:06:23,880
<b>I need to go.</b>

727
01:06:28,250 --> 01:06:30,660
<b>Things suddenly got busy at the homestay.</b>

728
01:06:30,960 --> 01:06:32,360
<b>Timing is so...</b>

729
01:06:36,700 --> 01:06:38,730
<b>It's working. Go to bed.</b>

730
01:06:40,900 --> 01:06:43,340
<b>Go before I get sleepier.</b>

731
01:06:46,210 --> 01:06:47,340
<b>I'll walk you home.</b>

732
01:06:58,050 --> 01:07:00,220
<b>No one will use that blanket,</b>

733
01:07:01,150 --> 01:07:03,360
<b>so come whenever you want to sleep well.</b>

734
01:07:05,230 --> 01:07:07,260
<b>Since I can't go to the semi-basement.</b>

735
01:07:12,370 --> 01:07:14,670
<b>I can hear the thoughts in your head.</b>

736
01:07:19,410 --> 01:07:21,070
<b>It is what you're thinking.</b>

737
01:07:22,710 --> 01:07:23,780
<b>You're right.</b>

738
01:07:52,470 --> 01:07:53,810
<b>- Hey. - Yes?</b>

739
01:07:54,210 --> 01:07:57,140
<b>Tell me 1 more of the 100 reasons why it can't happen.</b>

740
01:07:57,140 --> 01:07:59,180
<b>(Epilogue)</b>

741
01:08:01,180 --> 01:08:04,350
<b>See? You won't let me go.</b>

742
01:08:04,350 --> 01:08:06,120
<b>You want me too much.</b>

743
01:08:06,450 --> 01:08:08,660
<b>It's just for today. I only need you today.</b>

744
01:08:08,660 --> 01:08:10,120
<b>I won't need you starting tomorrow.</b>

745
01:08:11,590 --> 01:08:13,560
<b>I don't want to be alone today.</b>

746
01:08:14,130 --> 01:08:15,290
<b>I'm scared.</b>

747
01:08:24,440 --> 01:08:25,470
<b>Thumbs up.</b>

748
01:08:54,830 --> 01:08:57,400
<b>(A Piece of Your Mind)</b>

749
01:08:57,400 --> 01:08:58,670
<b>Out of the blue,</b>

750
01:08:58,670 --> 01:09:01,670
<b>there are 100 reasons why you can't like him.</b>

751
01:09:01,670 --> 01:09:02,940
<b>Was it intentional?</b>

752
01:09:02,940 --> 01:09:04,810
<b>Stopping midway and looking only briefly.</b>

753
01:09:04,810 --> 01:09:05,850
<b>Yes.</b>

754
01:09:05,850 --> 01:09:07,880
<b>What was your daughter's name?</b>

755
01:09:07,880 --> 01:09:09,920
<b>You know, a noose hanging from the ceiling.</b>

756
01:09:10,580 --> 01:09:11,580
<b>What?</b>

757
01:09:11,780 --> 01:09:12,850
<b>Ji Soo?</b>

758
01:09:13,590 --> 01:09:14,790
<b>Someone was just here.</b>

759
01:09:15,250 --> 01:09:17,360
<b>I'll make an exception and listen to you.</b>

760
01:09:17,720 --> 01:09:19,130
<b>As long as no one dies.</b>

761
01:09:19,530 --> 01:09:20,730
<b>What if someone did die?</b>

762
01:09:21,160 --> 01:09:23,330
<b>I want to see you and I want to stay with you.</b>

763
01:09:24,260 --> 01:09:25,970
<b>This is all new to me.</b>

